<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الدولة:</span> الكويت<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">الفاكس:</span> ٠٠٩٦٥٥٣٢٨٩٦<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
